26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_mc_g98.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:34 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "priv.h"
30
31static const struct nvkm_mc_intr
32g98_mc_intr[] = {
33 { 0x04000000, NVKM_ENGINE_DISP }, /* DISP first, so pageflip timestamps work */
34 { 0x00000001, NVKM_ENGINE_MSPPP },
35 { 0x00000100, NVKM_ENGINE_FIFO },
36 { 0x00001000, NVKM_ENGINE_GR },
37 { 0x00004000, NVKM_ENGINE_SEC }, /* NV84:NVA3 */
38 { 0x00008000, NVKM_ENGINE_MSVLD },
39 { 0x00020000, NVKM_ENGINE_MSPDEC },
40 { 0x00040000, NVKM_SUBDEV_PMU }, /* NVA3:NVC0 */
41 { 0x00080000, NVKM_SUBDEV_THERM }, /* NVA3:NVC0 */
42 { 0x00100000, NVKM_SUBDEV_TIMER },
43 { 0x00200000, NVKM_SUBDEV_GPIO }, /* PMGR->GPIO */
44 { 0x00200000, NVKM_SUBDEV_I2C }, /* PMGR->I2C/AUX */
45 { 0x00400000, NVKM_ENGINE_CE0 }, /* NVA3- */
46 { 0x10000000, NVKM_SUBDEV_BUS },
47 { 0x80000000, NVKM_ENGINE_SW },
48 { 0x0042d101, NVKM_SUBDEV_FB },
49 {},
50};
51
52static const struct nvkm_mc_func
53g98_mc = {
54 .init = nv50_mc_init,
55 .intr = g98_mc_intr,
56 .intr_unarm = nv04_mc_intr_unarm,
57 .intr_rearm = nv04_mc_intr_rearm,
58 .intr_mask = nv04_mc_intr_mask,
59};
60
61int
62g98_mc_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index, struct nvkm_mc **pmc)
63{
64 return nvkm_mc_new_(&g98_mc, device, index, pmc);
65}
